response.overview: One of the most wonderful legends of the Thousand and One Nights tells about a strange love story that grows between two beings, one of whom is from the human race and lives on land and is called Prince Noor and the other is a water creature that lives in the depths of the seas only and does not have two legs like a human being but a tail like fish and has a beautiful face just like the face of a beautiful human being called the princess Mermaid..
response.title: Fawazeer Sherihan
